{"tid":1316901,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我地而家需要既係法律戰 唔係勇武亦唔係文宣","createTime":"2019-07-14T16:58:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T18:08:15.000Z","uid":5822,"like":186,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"eb350d9a87e72368551547c92ab61727976183e0","tid":1316901,"uid":5822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:58:55.000Z","msg":"打記者 違反基本法新聞自由<br />\n打議員 <br />\n挑釁市民反洩 未能保持專業操守及政治中立 失職<br />\n違反武力指引及警察通例 （無委任證）<br />\n封路唔比去 非洲禁錮及有意圖謀殺<br />\n今晚擅闖私人地方  要住客屌先走 全部唔跟指引<br />\n<br />\n根本係要成個警務處連 保安局及律政司 加特首一齊告 佢地絕對責無旁貸 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">強烈建議搞一個世界支援反送中基金</span></span><br />\n支援香港既律司費同請一個好既大狀打 贏左既話絕對能夠打擊政府 <br />\n絕對唔可以比佢地做既咁既野無後果 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">我地要以司法打贏司法</span></span>還我法治之都！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">重申 我地無提及港獨 請3毛唔好係咪都將港獨帽子扣係我地身上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"9660cfae54b0432cb4183aff078c221616fcfcce","tid":1316901,"uid":238051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:01:12.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">你扮警察\n有人冒警\n我冇嘢講\n我要搵律師</code></pre>"},{"pid":"17f0cbb105f24f79fb9ac8852e59b52595be0507","tid":1316901,"uid":5822,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:07:38.000Z","msg":"絕對唔可以再比呢班中學雞程度都無既人揸槍"},{"pid":"9c872247c81bf3cf8b299a24e56f147c818d1496","tid":1316901,"uid":5822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:12:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07d16bc7746c4985ae711d560268c75c42139cf5","tid":1316901,"uid":5822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:16:20.000Z","msg":"推啦屌"},{"pid":"f5c0b2951f971b6e55c32b7167cbfb7da1270ade","tid":1316901,"uid":48868,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:17:21.000Z","msg":"求律師和法律L<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e10c784406e52affa84f3783adec8a0611ce4e1f","tid":1316901,"uid":28451,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:20:06.000Z","msg":"明白事理果啲其實都明晒，剩低都係弱智廢老<br />\n講道理嘅文宣差唔多已到盡頭，我覺得可以用無賴文宣<br />\n以子之矛攻子之盾，用返佢地個邏輯講<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">無賴文宣，正式啟動</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n學藍絲話齋，如果係外國，個警察死撚左喇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1316434\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1316434</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"df4d54d969cd324932a47f6ce550589c878ae73c","tid":1316901,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:20:58.000Z","msg":"文宣攻保皇：前線警中矢之的，偽建制派議員全部失蹤<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1316637\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1316637</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"300a8b166680c961475b8b268c4c71575cd42125","tid":1316901,"uid":5822,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"f5c0b2951f971b6e55c32b7167cbfb7da1270ade","tid":1316901,"uid":48868,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:17:21.000Z","msg":"求律師和法律L<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:30:42.000Z","msg":"我地只需要一個世界基金戶口 有錢就請外國超級大狀打到佢地仆街. 但要有個有公信力既大台開先會捐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"669e1d8f0cbbfb0c1c11438b603317a77d32cd32","tid":1316901,"uid":66390,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:31:25.000Z","msg":"點解唔可以同步<br />\n無衝突嫁喎"},{"pid":"a1d140471f6c5b15e4d756bab923779cb10be24b","tid":1316901,"uid":133519,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:33:46.000Z","msg":"重申 我地無提及港獨 請3毛唔好係咪都將港獨帽子扣係我地身上<br />\n<br />\n咪醜化獨立，獨立有咩問題"},{"pid":"dee1bbe8082c7a740fdaf6ab5b50c2371a112406","tid":1316901,"uid":58